name: Babywhale Rescue
description:
Rescue the babywhale trapped in an underwater cave system using the sonar sound of your submarine. 

HOW TO PLAY?
 > Rotate the submarine using ARROW KEYS.
 > Avoid the SEAWEEDS.
 > When babywhale is within the radius of the light, press SPACE to attract it.

SOUND CREDITS: https://www.zapsplat.com/

Made for GDKO game jam ROUND-2.
